      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and remains a dependable choice for daily transportation. While the engine and mechanical components are sound, the exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, paint fading on the hood, and a few minor door dings. The interior is clean but exhibits typical wear on the upholstery and floor mats. It\u2019s a solid, functional car for someone prioritizing utility over aesthetics.",
