      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This expertly maintained vehicle presents a compelling opportunity for the sophisticated buyer. It demonstrates consistent mechanical performance and a high degree of aesthetic care, ensuring a driving experience characterized by both comfort and reliability. Having undergone a rigorous professional assessment, this motorcar is prepared for immediate service, offering exceptional value and structural integrity.",
      "price": 34800.0,
